## ğŸ” Environment Variables

```bash
# Server
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=5000

# Database
MONGO_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/officesphere

# JWT
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
JWT_EXPIRE=7d

# Frontend
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000
```
